# Mac filesystem metadata
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# Editor / IDE artifacts
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Obsidian workspace state
.obsidian/workspace*
.obsidian/cache
.obsidian/graph.json

# OS / network artifacts
Thumbs.db
.directory

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Personal design work — excluded by default so this folder can be shared
# without leaking active design conversations.
#
# TRADE-OFF: the OV's core thesis is "state lives in files." Excluding
# _design-state.md and Sessions/*.md by default means YOUR own design
# history is NOT version-controlled unless you opt in. To track your own
# cartridge, see INSTALL.md § "Tracking your own design history" — there
# is a copy-paste `git add -f` recipe there. Edit this section to flip
# the default if you'd rather track-by-default.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------

# Design-state files: live record of where each design engagement stands
**/_design-state.md

# Optional user profile
_USER.md

# Personal cartridges — exclude session content and decision logs by default.
# To track your own cartridge, use `git add -f` on the specific paths.
**/Sessions/*.md
!**/Sessions/.gitkeep

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Always tracked (overrides above for the shipped worked examples):
# The five shipped cartridges demonstrate the system and their contents
# are part of the release.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
!SOLVE-eX-Retrospective/**
!LifeLong-Learning-Retrospective/**
!Negotiation-Preparation/**
!Long-Form-Writing/**
!Relationship-Cultivation/**
